@startuml
' NutriSurvey - Sequence Diagram
' Actors & Boundaries (Auth)
actor User as Pengguna
boundary "UI Splash Screen\n(P011)" as Splash
boundary "UI Sign In Sign Up\n(P012)" as SignInUp
boundary "UI Daftar Akun\n(P013)" as DaftarAkun
boundary "UI Verifikasi Email\n(P014)" as VerifEmail
boundary "UI Selamat Datang\n(P015)" as Welcome
boundary "UI Dashboard\n(P016)" as Dashboard

' Actors & Boundaries (Konsumsi)
boundary "UI Pilih Waktu Makan\n(P002)" as PilihWaktu
boundary "UI Pilih Makanan\n(P003)" as PilihMakanan
boundary "UI Catat Manual\n(P004)" as CatatManual
boundary "UI Data Tersimpan\n(P006)" as DataTersimpan

' Actors & Boundaries (Rekomendasi)
boundary "UI Rekomendasi Menu\n(P007)" as RekMenu
boundary "UI Preferensi Anda\n(P008)" as PrefAnda
boundary "UI Atur Preferensi\n(P009)" as AturPref
boundary "UI Menu Rekomendasi\n(P010)" as MenuRek

' Controllers & Entities
control ControllerAutentikasi as AuthController
control ControllerDashboard as DashController
control ControllerKonsumsi as KonsController
control ControllerRekomendasi as RekController

entity Pengguna as Pengguna
entity Sesi as Sesi
entity EmailVerifikasi as EmailVerif
entity MenuMakan as MenuMakan
entity BeratBadan as BeratBadan
entity KonsumsiHarian as KonsumsiHarian
entity PreferensiPengguna as PrefPengguna
entity ProfilNutrisi as ProfilNutrisi
entity RekomendasiMenu as RekMenuEnt

' ============================================================
' FLOW AUTH: Register & Login
' ============================================================
== Alur Auth: Register & Login ==

Pengguna -> Splash: Buka aplikasi
Pengguna -> Splash: Tombol DAFTAR
Splash -> DaftarAkun: Navigasi ke tab Sign Up

Pengguna -> DaftarAkun: Isi form (nama, email, password)
Pengguna -> DaftarAkun: Klik DAFTAR
DaftarAkun -> AuthController: POST /auth/register
AuthController -> Pengguna: findByEmail(email)
Pengguna --> AuthController: null / user
AuthController -> EmailVerifikasi: crypto.randomBytes(32) → token
EmailVerifikasi --> AuthController: token_verifikasi
AuthController -> Pengguna: create({ nama, email, password_hash, token })
Pengguna --> AuthController: { id, tokenVerifikasi }
AuthController -> AuthController: jwt.sign({ userId }) → JWT token
AuthController -> Sesi: JWT tersimpan di localStorage
AuthController --> DaftarAkun: { success: true, data: { token, user } }
DaftarAkun --> VerifEmail: Redirect ke verifikasi email

Pengguna -> VerifEmail: Buka link verifikasi dari email
VerifEmail -> AuthController: GET /auth/verify-email/:token
AuthController -> EmailVerifikasi: SELECT * FROM pengguna WHERE token_verifikasi = ?
EmailVerifikasi --> AuthController: { id, nama, email }
AuthController -> Pengguna: UPDATE email_terverifikasi = 1, token_verifikasi = NULL
Pengguna --> AuthController: { id, nama, email }
AuthController --> Welcome: { success: true }

Pengguna -> Welcome: Isi email & password
Pengguna -> Welcome: Klik MASUK
Welcome -> AuthController: POST /auth/login
AuthController -> Pengguna: findByEmail(email)
Pengguna --> AuthController: user
AuthController -> AuthController: bcrypt.compare(password, hash)
AuthController -> Sesi: jwt.sign({ userId }) → session token
Sesi --> AuthController: JWT (7d expiry)
AuthController --> Welcome: { success: true, data: { token, user } }
AuthController -> Sesi: Token disimpan via API.setToken()
Welcome --> Dashboard: Navigasi ke dashboard

' Controllers
control ControllerKonsumsi as KonsController
control ControllerRekomendasi as RekController

' Entities
entity MenuMakan as MenuMakan
entity KonsumsiHarian as KonsumsiHarian
entity PreferensiPengguna as PrefPengguna
entity ProfilNutrisi as ProfilNutrisi
entity RekomendasiMenu as RekMenuEnt

' ============================================================
' FLOW A: Catat Makanan via Pencarian Database
' ============================================================
== Alur A: Catat dari Database ==

Pengguna -> PilihWaktu: Pilih waktu makan (Sarapan/Siang/Malam)
PilihWaktu -> PilihMakanan: LANJUT

Pengguna -> PilihMakanan: Input keyword pencarian
PilihMakanan -> KonsController: GET /konsumsi/search?keyword=
KonsController -> MenuMakan: search(keyword)
MenuMakan --> KonsController: [rows menu_makanan]
KonsController --> PilihMakanan: { data: [...] }

Pengguna -> PilihMakanan: Pilih item makanan

Pengguna -> PilihMakanan: Atur porsi, SIMPAN
PilihMakanan -> KonsController: POST /konsumsi/simpan
KonsController -> KonsumsiHarian: create({ userId, menuId, porsi, ... })
KonsumsiHarian --> KonsController: insertId
KonsController --> DataTersimpan: { success: true, data: {...} }
DataTersimpan --> Pengguna: Tampilkan konfirmasi

Pengguna -> DataTersimpan: TAMBAH LAGI
DataTersimpan --> PilihWaktu: Kembali ke P002

Pengguna -> DataTersimpan: KE BERANDA
DataTersimpan --> Dashboard: Navigasi

' ============================================================
' FLOW B: Catat Manual
' ============================================================
== Alur B: Catat Manual ==

Pengguna -> PilihWaktu: Pilih waktu makan
PilihWaktu -> CatatManual: Pilih "Catat Manual"

Pengguna -> CatatManual: Isi form (nama, kalori, protein, lemak, karbo)
Pengguna -> CatatManual: Klik SIMPAN
CatatManual -> KonsController: POST /konsumsi/simpan
KonsController -> KonsumsiHarian: create({ userId, nama_makanan, kalori, ... })
KonsumsiHarian --> KonsController: insertId
KonsController --> DataTersimpan: { success: true, data: {...} }
DataTersimpan --> Pengguna: Tampilkan konfirmasi

' ============================================================
' FLOW C: Rekomendasi Menu
' ============================================================
== Alur C: Rekomendasi Menu ==

Pengguna -> RekMenu: Buka Rekomendasi Menu
Pengguna -> RekMenu: BERIKAN REKOMENDASI
RekMenu -> RekController: GET /rekomendasi

RekController -> PrefPengguna: getByUser(userId)
PrefPengguna --> RekController: { preferensi_makan, target_kalori, ... }

RekController -> KonsumsiHarian: getByUserAndDate(userId, today)
KonsumsiHarian --> RekController: todayConsumption

RekController -> MenuMakan: getAll()
MenuMakan --> RekController: allMenus

RekController -> RekController: Filter & sort by sisa kalori + preferensi
RekController --> RekMenuEnt: { rekomendasi, sisaKalori }
RekController --> RekMenu: { data: { rekomendasi, sisaKalori, ... } }
RekMenu --> Pengguna: Tampilkan rekomendasi + sisa kalori

Pengguna -> PrefAnda: ATUR PREFERENSI
PrefAnda -> AturPref: Navigasi
Pengguna -> AturPref: Isi form preferensi
Pengguna -> AturPref: SIMPAN PREFERENSI
AturPref -> RekController: POST /rekomendasi/preferensi
RekController -> PrefPengguna: upsert(userId, data)
PrefPengguna --> RekController: { id / updated }
RekController --> AturPref: { success: true }
AturPref --> Pengguna: Toast "Preferensi berhasil disimpan"

Pengguna -> MenuRek: Lihat rekomendasi lengkap
MenuRek -> RekController: GET /rekomendasi (di-fetch ulang)
RekController -> MenuMakan: getAll() + filter
RekController --> MenuRek: { data: { rekomendasi, ... } }
MenuRek --> Pengguna: Tampilkan Top 3 + Best Match

Pengguna -> MenuRek: Catat Pilihan
MenuRek -> KonsController: POST /konsumsi/simpan
KonsController -> KonsumsiHarian: create(...)
KonsController --> MenuRek: { success: true }

' ============================================================
' FLOW D: Dashboard — Load data
' ============================================================
== Alur D: Dashboard Data Tercatat (P024) ==

Pengguna -> Dashboard: Navigasi ke dashboard
Dashboard -> DashController: GET /dashboard
DashController -> KonsumsiHarian: getByUserAndDate(userId, today)
KonsumsiHarian --> DashController: todayConsumption
DashController -> KonsumsiHarian: getByUserAndPeriod(userId, startDate, endDate)
KonsumsiHarian --> DashController: weeklyConsumption
DashController -> BeratBadan: getLatest(userId)
BeratBadan --> DashController: latestWeight
DashController -> BeratBadan: getByUser(userId)
BeratBadan --> DashController: allWeights
DashController -> PreferensiPengguna: getByUser(userId)
PreferensiPengguna --> DashController: { target_kalori }
DashController -> DashController: Hitung total kalori, protein, lemak, karbo
DashController -> DashController: Hitung mingguan, BB trend, rekomendasi
DashController --> Dashboard: { data: { kalori_terpakai, nutrisi_makro, mingguan, makanan_hari_ini, berat_badan, rekomendasi } }
Dashboard --> Pengguna: Render card kalori + circular progress
Dashboard --> Pengguna: Render nutrisi makro bars
Dashboard --> Pengguna: Render makanan per waktu
Dashboard --> Pengguna: Render BB + chart
Dashboard --> Pengguna: Render minggu ini summary
Dashboard --> Pengguna: Render rekomendasi
Dashboard --> Pengguna: Render menu utama + bottom nav

@enduml
